rows.label: fev06_040_175_msg0001
rows.name: Beyond this point is the summit venue.

rows.label: fev06_040_175_msg0002
rows.name:
I must apologize, but only
official national representatives
are permitted beyond this point.

rows.label: fev06_040_175_msg0003
rows.name: This is as far as we go.

rows.label: fev06_040_175_msg0004
rows.name:
Yes...
Kagutsuchi and
I shall proceed to the meeting.

rows.label: fev06_040_175_msg0005
rows.name: I'll go with you.

rows.label: fev06_040_175_msg0006
rows.name:
Wait, you're not allowed in,
Turtle-chan.

rows.label: fev06_040_175_msg0007
rows.name: Whaddya mean?

rows.label: fev06_040_175_msg0008
rows.name:
I'm the prince of Luxuria, ya know.
That makes me
the official representative.

rows.label: fev06_040_175_msg0009
rows.name:
Oh, right...
I forgot.

rows.label: fev06_040_175_msg0010
rows.name: That's pretty harsh, ya know...

rows.label: fev06_040_175_msg0011
rows.name:
Sorry, sorry.
For a prince,
you're quite approachable.

rows.label: fev06_040_175_msg0012
rows.name: Well, whatever...

rows.label: fev06_040_175_msg0013
rows.name: Hikari, you should come too.

rows.label: fev06_040_175_msg0014
rows.name: I suppose...

rows.label: fev06_040_175_msg0015
rows.name:
I'm not exactly thrilled about it,
but I have a role to play here.

rows.label: fev06_040_175_msg0016
rows.name:
Rex, you head back to our chambers
with the others and wait for us.

rows.label: fev06_040_175_msg0017
rows.name: Sure thing!

rows.label: fev06_040_175_msg0018
rows.name:
Who's supposed to be
the babysitter here...

rows.label: fev06_040_175_msg0019
rows.name: I wonder who indeed?

rows.label: fev06_040_175_msg0020
rows.name: Right. Sure.

rows.label: fev06_040_175_msg0021
rows.name: Take care in there, Hikari...

rows.label: fev06_040_175_msg0022
rows.name:
Don't worry...
I can handle this.
